Denizen Men Blue Polo T-shirt :
Denizen brings you a smart Polo T-shirt in blue colour. This comfortable T-shirt is a great addition to your collection of casual wear and is perfect for the summer season. The Polo tee has the brand logo embroidered on the chest and features a ribbed collar and half sleeves. To complete your look for an evening at the club wear this T-shirt with a pair of black jeans canvas shoes and sport a cool watch.
